  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The ARS-WiFi6E-M2 is an indoor omni antenna that supports the 2.4GHz, 5GHz, and 6GHz frequency bands. ARS-WiFi6E-M2 is perfect for use in homes, offices, and other indoor environments. It has a gain of 5 dBi and can be used to improve the signal strength of your Wi-Fi network, extend the range of your network, or eliminate dead spots. The ARS-WiFi6E-M2 is compatible with a wide range of Wi-Fi routers with RP-SMA Female ports."
    }
